in the Supplementary Note II, using the analysis tools
that we employ to discuss temperature chaos.
The main difference will be in that in the compu
tation of ζ(t1, t2) the spin configurations of the single
replica are compared at times t1 and t2. Instead, here
we shall be considering two independent replicas, one
